            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Sabemos cómo repetir código usando un bucle <code>while</code>. Como este programa que repite declaraciones para mostrar la bandera estadounidense.</p><code name=\"main.swift\" version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\"><content><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" firstCounter = \" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" firstCounter &lt; \" /><text value=\"5\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" { \" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;**********---------&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  firstCounter += \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"var\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" secondCounter = \" /><text value=\"0\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"while\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" secondCounter &lt; \" /><text value=\"4\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;-------------------&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  secondCounter += \" /><text value=\"1\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"**********---------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"**********---------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"**********---------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"**********---------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"**********---------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"-------------------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"-------------------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"-------------------\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"-------------------\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
